Summary: I WAS TAKING PICTURES OF THE SUNSET FROM THE TOP OF MY ROOF AND ONLY SEEN THIS OBJECT WHEN I PUT THE PICTURE ON MY COMPUTER.
divs: sighting detailsi was taking pictures of the sunset from the top of my roof on my house. when i put the pictures into my computer that's when i noticed an object in one of the photos - the photo was straight above my head\house and didn't even hear it at the time of taking the photo. the object above me was round with a inner round circle in the middle of it. it looked grey\silver color. (information moved to fi box) cms 11\16\11 13:20 cst flg i will be sending him 3 photos today.
